<component id="ID_poptext1">
  	<text><![CDATA[<b>This is the first step in the risk management process. It determines the quantitative and qualitative value of risk related to a specific situation or recognized threat.</b>]]></text> 
</component>

<component id="ID_poptext2">
	<text><![CDATA[<b>A document that addresses the constraints and behaviors of members of an organization and often specifies how data can be accessed and what data is accessible by whom.</b>]]></text>
</component>

<component id="ID_poptext3">
  	<text><![CDATA[<b>This is the governance model set out by an organization for information security.</b>]]></text> 
</component>

<component id="ID_poptext4">
  	<text><![CDATA[<b>This is an inventory of and classification scheme for information assets.</b>]]></text> 
</component>

<component id="ID_poptext5">
  	<text><![CDATA[<b>This addresses security procedures relating to employees joining, moving within, and leaving an organization.</b>]]></text> 
</component>

<component id="ID_poptext6">
	<text><![CDATA[<b>This describes the protection of the computer facilities within an organization.</b>]]></text>
</component>

<component id="ID_poptext7">
  	<text><![CDATA[<b>This describes the management of technical security controls in systems and networks.</b>]]></text> 
</component>

<component id="ID_poptext8">
  	<text><![CDATA[<b>This describes the restriction of access rights to networks, systems, applications, functions, and data.</b>]]></text> 
</component>

<component id="ID_poptext9">
  	<text><![CDATA[<b>This describes the integration of security into applications.</b>]]></text> 
</component>

<component id="ID_poptext10">
	<text><![CDATA[<b>This describes how to anticipate and respond to information security breaches.</b>]]></text>
</component>

<component id="ID_poptext11">
  	<text><![CDATA[<b>This describes the protection, maintenance, and recovery of business-critical processes and systems.</b>]]></text> 
</component>

<component id="ID_poptext12">
  	<text><![CDATA[<b>This describes the process of ensuring conformance with information security policies, standards, and regulations.</b>]]></text> 
</component>

